   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Side 1: Ptolemaeus to Heraclides, greeting. If you are well, and if the objects of your care and other concerns are to your mind I should be glad, and much gratitude would be due to the gods; I myself am also in good health. You will oblige me...  (Grenfell &amp; Hunt)</ab>
